WEBVTT

00:04:28.429 --> 00:04:31.813
And there was so much power

00:04:31.837 --> 00:04:33.340
in this patchwork.

00:04:33.904 --> 00:04:36.431
It provided a natural mechanism

00:04:36.455 --> 00:04:40.004
to resist the spread of future fires
across the landscape.

00:04:41.002 --> 00:04:43.148
Once a patch of forest burned,

00:04:43.172 --> 00:04:46.447
it helped to prevent the flow
of fire across the landscape.

00:04:47.046 --> 00:04:48.537
A way to think about it is,

00:04:48.561 --> 00:04:53.124
the burned patches
helped the rest of the forest

00:04:53.148 --> 00:04:55.176
to be forest.

00:04:56.677 --> 00:04:58.528
Let's add humans to the mix.

00:04:59.144 --> 00:05:02.869
For 10,000 years, Native Americans
lived on this landscape,